message.content:
I need to identify and extract the specific line items and value of amounts of interest accrued but not yet received from the balance sheet.

In a balance sheet, interest accrued but not yet received is typically shown as "Interest Receivable" or a similar account name.

Looking at the provided balance sheet, I can see there is indeed a line item called "Interest Receivable" with the following values:
- Initial amount: 0.00 (as of 2023-12-31)
- End amount: 7775.44 (as of 2024-02-04)

This represents interest that has been earned but not yet collected as of the respective dates.

```json
{"solution": {'initial value': '0.00', 'end value': '7775.44'}}
```
